DocAttribute.Name: ComponentOfTotal
DocAttribute.Documentation: The applied value (total or subtotal) of which the value being considered is a component.

DocAttribute.Name: Components
DocAttribute.Documentation: Applied values that are components of another applied value and from which that applied value may be deduced.

DocAttribute.Name: ArithmeticOperator
DocAttribute.Documentation: The arithmetic operator applied in an applied value relationship.

DocAttribute.Name: Name
DocAttribute.Documentation: A name used to identify or qualify the applied value relationship.

DocAttribute.Name: Description
DocAttribute.Documentation: A description that may apply additional information about an applied value relationship.
